<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2018-11-16</DATELINE><TITLE>Infectious Diseases and Agriculture</TITLE><BODY>• Agriculture has huge impacts on human health, both positive and negative; • Agriculture has not been oriented to achieving health outcomes; • The livestock sector creates a disproportionate share of risks and benefits; • Health problems related to farming and food require solutions that include these sectors.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>